{"tid":1132183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港最敢反共嘅藝人連登仔都封殺","createTime":"2019-04-30T06:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T07:50:30.000Z","uid":188657,"like":9,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"502ba668ff70b5778527570027c8b4530d056273","tid":1132183,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"咁仲有邊個藝人敢反共呢？？<br />\n講真有邊個藝人好似杜汶澤咁大大聲反共？？<br />\n你哋反杜汶澤嘅人 知唔知你哋做緊幾錯嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n一件咁無聊嘅事竟然有一班人凌晨洗板  想用一件咁嘅事嚟叫人全面抵制杜汶澤 我覺得好荒謬<br />\n<br />\n佢個助手遲出糧 糧己出 歉又道咗 追擊班人係有心趕盡殺絕<br />\n<br />\n夠膽反共嘅藝人幾乎已經冇 希望你哋唔好咁容易畀人煽動"},{"pid":"e5f4d0fa4cdcbad8ad15dc29727f8004d95b111a","tid":1132183,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"因為反共就接受佢任何on9同碌柒行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54f1cf1bc2ed3531cf75fb0f6be9afcdd6d16b7","tid":1132183,"uid":80015,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"你估反佢既係咩人"},{"pid":"d6d275fb4b552c0ac01c3b10cfa8ca5b0acc964f","tid":1132183,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"何韻思"},{"pid":"da2ee0d03847023b887b4defa27b21a414a6aa77","tid":1132183,"uid":188657,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e5f4d0fa4cdcbad8ad15dc29727f8004d95b111a","tid":1132183,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"因為反共就接受佢任何on9同碌柒行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"因為on9同碌柒所以要全面封殺同追擊佢？？你嘅理由會唔會太牽強？ 佢而家只係下屬遲出糧畀人 而唔係殺咗人 佢犯咗彌天大罪 ？"},{"pid":"ab1ff68a62ef8b8d5d77614eaa75a58da99cddf2","tid":1132183,"uid":129622,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da2ee0d03847023b887b4defa27b21a414a6aa77","tid":1132183,"uid":188657,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e5f4d0fa4cdcbad8ad15dc29727f8004d95b111a","tid":1132183,"uid":196924,"like":7,"d